*** Keywords ***
Install UI Plugin
    [Arguments]  ${ova-ip}  ${plugin_preset}  ${vc}=%{TEST_URL}  ${vc_user}=%{TEST_USERNAME}  ${vc_pass}=%{TEST_PASSWORD}  ${vc_thumbprint}=${TEST_THUMBPRINT}
