    ${status}=  Call UI API With Preset  ${ova-ip}  install  ${plugin_preset}  ${vc}  ${vc_user}  ${vc_pass}  ${vc_thumbprint}
    Should Be Equal As Integers  ${status}  ${ok}

    [Return]  ${status}

